    <Descriptive_Notes>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>Temporary, heat-resistant, cohesive, porous molds that capture the fine impression of a model to be reproduced and forms the void into which a molten material will be cast. Investment, green sand, and ceramic shell are examples of refractory molds.</Note_Text>
